      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a specimen of unrivaled integrity. Professional inspections are welcomed to confirm its pristine state.",
