      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) that defines showroom-standard preservation. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transient response. The Getrag six-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is superlative, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and Bilstein-damped suspension that retains its original factory geometry. Every system, from the high-pressure double-VANOS to the cross-drilled braking assembly, operates within exacting tolerances. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen for the collector demanding mechanical purity and uncompromised performance.",
